        "Karishma Beauty Salon": "The Context: Located just off Artesia's famous Pioneer Boulevard\u2014the cultural and commercial heart of Southern California's Indian American community\u2014this salon has been a local staple for over two decades.\n\nThe Business: Founded by Parul Gandhi, it is a quintessential representation of the highly specialized, cultural businesses that thrive in this enclave. It serves as a go-to community hub for traditional Indian beauty services, ranging from expert threading and henna applications to highly intricate bridal makeup.",
