        "Azteca Tire & Auto Repair": "Local auto repair shop on Eagle Rock Blvd.",
        "Bon Temps Cottages (True Blood filming location)": "Residential cottages featured as the exterior of Merlotte's Bar in the television show True Blood.",
        "Brad Spence Studio": "Artist studio on Eagle Vista Drive.",
        "Casa Lu-An Motel": "Classic mid-century motel on Colorado Blvd.",
        "Chevy Chase Canyon Entrance": "A primary access point to one of Glendale's oldest and most scenic canyon neighborhoods, known for its mid-century hillside homes.",
