        "Eagle Rock (The Landmark)": "The Eagle Rock formation is a natural volcanic rock outcropping that gives the neighborhood its name. The shadow of a giant eagle is cast on its face at certain times of day, a phenomenon observed by indigenous peoples for millennia before the arrival of European settlers.",
