        "Los Angeles Ostrich Farm": "Located right next door to the Alligator Farm, this was the direct competitor to South Pasadena's Cawston Farm. It offered similar ostrich-drawn carriage rides and photo opportunities with the giant birds, capitalizing on the \"animal row\" that developed along Mission Road.",
        "Mi Barra Deportes Bar": "Local sports bar on N San Fernando Rd.",
