        "Dingbat Apartment Building": "A classic example of Dingbat architecture.",
        "Dunsmuir Flats": "Architect: Gregory Ain\n\nArchitectural Style: International Style\n\nThe History: Designated as Los Angeles Historic-Cultural Monument #954, this complex is a premier example of Gregory Ain's commitment to providing high-quality, modern, affordable housing.\n\nKey Architectural Features: The site consists of four interconnected units stepped along the slope to ensure maximum privacy for each balcony and garden. It is characterized by smooth white stucco walls and continuous ribbon windows that flood the units with natural light.",
