        "Big Dean's Ocean Front Cafe": "Big Dean's Ocean Front Cafe. A landmark on the boardwalk since the 1970s (previously Loring's Lunchroom in 1902), it has served famous patrons like Arnold Schwarzenegger and Cary Grant. While the cafe itself is a staple, it is located directly at the foot of the Santa Monica Pier, a setting for countless films including The Sting, Forrest Gump, and The Net.",
