        "McGroarty Arts Center": "The Arts & Crafts-era home of John Steven McGroarty, California's Poet Laureate and author of the famous 'Mission Play.' The property reflects the Arroyo Culture aesthetic that flourished in the foothills communities of the early 20th century.",
        "McGroarty Arts Center Neighborhood": "Located near the historic home of poet John Steven McGroarty, this area is a hub for local arts in the Verdugo Mountains.",
